6. API Endpoints
Users
•	POST /api/users → Register new user
•	GET /api/users/:id → Get user profile
•	PUT /api/users/:id/badges → Update badges
Clubs
•	GET /api/clubs → Fetch all clubs
•	POST /api/clubs → Create a new club
•	PUT /api/clubs/:id/join → Join a club
Events
•	GET /api/events → List all events
•	POST /api/events → Create an event
•	PUT /api/events/:id/rsvp → RSVP to an event
News
•	GET /api/news → Fetch news posts
•	POST /api/news → Add a news article
________________________________________
7. Workflows
Student
1.	Log in using college Google account
2.	Join clubs of interest
3.	RSVP for events
4.	Post in forums & gain badges
Club Admin
1.	Create a club (select category)
2.	Manage members and approve join requests
3.	Organize events and track attendance
4.	Publish news & announcements
